---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me // haddnist"
	description="Public accountability, devlog, and systems engineering journey."
	pubDate={new Date('July 01 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Hello! I am <strong>haddnist</strong>. I built this site as a public accountability dashboard and engineering log.
	</p>

	<p>
		My primary focus is mastering low-level systems programming, high-performance concurrency, and memory safety. Currently, I am undertaking the <strong>KAIST Concurrency Course</strong> and working through the interactive edition of the <strong>Brown University Rust Book</strong>.
	</p>

	<p>
		By keeping my goals, daily sprint checklists, and architectural notes 100% public, I maintain extreme discipline and consistency. Whether shipping code, debugging borrow checker errors, or studying concurrent memory models, everything is logged here.
	</p>

	<p>
		Feel free to check out my daily progress in the <a href="/diary">Diary & Tasks</a> section or explore my technical writings in the <a href="/blog">Blog</a>!
	</p>
</Layout>
